ble integration</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"58c648a3-6c85-49f8-a7b9-549736774f00\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"me0346f1-jposh5-001\">Payment Flow</h2><p data-block-id=\"me03jl26-epjva1-005\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/TH%20Payment%20Flow-TrueMoney.mp4\" mediatype=\"video\" alt=\"TH Payment Flow-TrueMoney.mp4\" title=\"TH Payment Flow-TrueMoney.mp4\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-krfz54-047\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-89tuoa-048\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-q75iuk-049\">On the checkout page, end customers select TrueMoney E-Wallet </p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-3p8i9y-050\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-xjyydx-051\">Redirect end customers to web app &amp; end customers need to input registered mobile phone with TrueMoney E-Wallet</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-3p8i9y-050\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-xjyydx-051\">End customer submit OTP verification</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-3p8i9y-050\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-xjyydx-051\">Once OTP verification is completed, the payment will be paid successfully</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"me2wzdm5-yb8szd-001\"></p>","SeoTitle":"TrueMoney E-Wallet","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"TrueMoney E-Wallet","Slug":"truemoney-test-1","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[dat