<p data-block-id=\"e5668c92-7f76-44a7-880d-2c1bbbeaa024\"><strong>Integrasi yang kompatibel</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"58c648a3-6c85-49f8-a7b9-549736774f00\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"me0346f1-jposh5-001\">Alur Pembayaran</h2><p data-block-id=\"me03jl26-epjva1-005\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/TH%20Payment%20Flow-TrueMoney.mp4\" mediatype=\"video\" alt=\"TH Payment Flow-TrueMoney.mp4\" title=\"TH Payment Flow-TrueMoney.mp4\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-krfz54-047\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-89tuoa-048\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-q75iuk-049\">Di halaman checkout, pelanggan akhir memilih TrueMoney E-Wallet </p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-3p8i9y-050\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-xjyydx-051\">Arahkan pelanggan akhir ke aplikasi web &amp; pelanggan akhir perlu memasukkan nomor ponsel yang terdaftar di TrueMoney E-Wallet</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-3p8i9y-050\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-xjyydx-051\">Pelanggan akhir mengirimkan verifikasi OTP</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-3p8i9y-050\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wi5uw-xjyydx-051\">Setelah verifikasi OTP selesai, pembayaran akan berhasil dibayarkan</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"me2wzdm5-yb8szd-001\"></p>","SeoTitle":"TrueMoney E-Wallet","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ทรูมันนี่ อี-วอลเล็ท","Slug":"truemoney-test-1","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-